material BlackPlastic 0.04 0.038 0.034 roughness 0.36 specular 0.6 clearcoat 0.25 clearcoatRoughness 0.22
material StainlessSteel 1.0 0.98 0.94 roughness 0.025 metallic 1
material ChairChrome 0.96 0.95 0.92 roughness 0.012 metallic 0.45 specular 1 clearcoat 1 clearcoatRoughness 0.018
